ifferent emotional moods work for different people.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Different emotional moods work\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"different people\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When you are in a new coaching set-up this is stuff that you figure out along the way.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new coaching set\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Nobody in this life, including athletes, are perfect.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"this life\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But all you can do when that happens is just to learn from it and not make the same mistake and keep it moving.'\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same mistake\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith has clinched three Olympic medals to date, which have all come in the team-based 4\\u00d7100m relay event.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"three Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"the team-based 4\\u00d7100m relay event\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside her teammates, Asher-Smith won silver at Paris 2024, improving on back-to-back bronze medals at Tokyo 2020 and Rio 2016.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1285},